<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Tutorial — KeepLive</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #080808;
    --card:  #111111;
    --neon:  #ff2d55;
    --neon2: #ff6b00;
    --gold:  #ffd700;
    --white: #f0f0f0;
    --gray:  #888;
    --border: rgba(255,45,85,0.22);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── GLOW BG ── */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 35% at 50% 0%, rgba(255,45,85,.13) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 25% at 90% 80%, rgba(255,107,0,.07) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .page { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px 80px; }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 52px 0 36px;
  }

  .logo-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .15em;
    color: var(--neon); text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .logo-badge::before, .logo-badge::after {
    content: ''; display: block;
    width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--neon); opacity: .5;
  }

  header h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 11vw, 6rem);
    letter-spacing: .04em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  header p {
    font-size: .9rem; color: var(--gray);
    margin-top: 10px; letter-spacing: .04em;
  }

  /* ── VIDEO ── */
  .video-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(255,45,85,.12), 0 24px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    background: #000;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
  }

  .video-wrap video {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    display: block; object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .divider::before, .divider::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,45,85,.3), transparent);
  }
  .divider span {
    font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .18em;
    color: var(--neon); text-transform: uppercase; white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── CTA CARDS ── */
  .cta-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 28px 22px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }

  .cta-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(255,45,85,.18);
  }

  .cta-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(255,45,85,.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* card destaque (segundo) */
  .cta-card.featured {
    border-color: rgba(255,107,0,.4);
  }
  .cta-card.featured::before {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(255,107,0,.09) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .card-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: .6rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .card-tag.red   { background: rgba(255,45,85,.18); color: var(--neon); }
  .card-tag.gold  { background: rgba(255,215,0,.14); color: var(--gold); }

  .cta-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: .04em;
    margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    font-size: .78rem; color: #aaa; line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 22px; flex: 1;
  }

  .cta-card .price-block {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-card .de {
    font-size: .72rem; color: var(--gray);
    text-decoration: line-through; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .cta-card .por {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem; line-height: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--neon), var(--neon2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
  }

  .cta-card.featured .por {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--neon2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
  }

  .cta-card .pix {
    font-size: .65rem; color: #666; margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .btn-cta {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 13px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: .78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform .15s, box-shadow .15s;
  }

  .btn-cta.red {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--neon), var(--neon2));
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,45,85,.35);
  }

  .btn-cta.gold-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c9a800, #ff6b00);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,107,0,.35);
  }

  .btn-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-cta.red:hover   { box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(255,45,85,.55); }
  .btn-cta.gold-btn:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(255,107,0,.55); }

  /* ── TRUST ROW ── */
  .trust-row {
    display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .trust-row span {
    font-size: .7rem; color: #555;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 56px;
    font-size: .68rem; color: #333;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .cta-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    header h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header>
    <div class="logo-badge">KeepLive</div>
    <h1>Tutorial</h1>
    <p>Assista com atenção — cada detalhe importa.</p>
  </header>

  <!-- VIDEO -->
  <div class="video-wrap">
    <video controls playsinline preload="metadata"
      poster="">
      <source src="https://keeplive.vercel.app/videos/tutorial.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
      Seu navegador não suporta vídeo HTML5.
    </video>
  </div>

  <!-- DIVISOR -->
  <div class="divider"><span>Aproveite e turbine seus resultados</span></div>

  <!-- CTA CARDS -->
  <div class="cta-grid">

    <!-- Card 1 — Vídeos Virais -->
    <div class="cta-card">
      <div class="card-tag red">🔥 Mais popular</div>
      <h3>Pack 50.000 Vídeos Virais</h3>
      <p>Vídeos já validados pelo algoritmo, prontos para postar. Aumente seus espectadores em até <strong>+340%</strong> sem editar nada.</p>
      <div class="price-block">
        <span class="de">De R$ 97,00</span>
        <div class="por">R$ 27,90</div>
        <div class="pix">pagamento único · acesso imediato</div>
      </div>
      <a class="btn-cta red" href="https://go.perfectpay.com.br/PPU38CQCOQ0" target="_blank">
        🚀 Quero o pack agora
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 — Guia de Lucratividade -->
    <div class="cta-card featured">
      <div class="card-tag gold">💰 Maximize sua renda</div>
      <h3>Guia de Lucratividade</h3>
      <p>Estratégias comprovadas para transformar sua live em renda consistente — do zero até os <strong>R$ 4.200/mês</strong>.</p>
      <div class="price-block">
        <span class="de">De R$ 47,00</span>
        <div class="por">R$ 14,90</div>
        <div class="pix">pagamento único · acesso imediato</div>
      </div>
      <a class="btn-cta gold-btn" href="https://go.perfectpay.com.br/PPU38CQC90E" target="_blank">
        📈 Quero o guia agora
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- TRUST -->
  <div class="trust-row">
    <span>🔒 Pagamento 100% seguro</span>
    <span>⚡ Acesso imediato</span>
    <span>📧 Enviado por e-mail</span>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <p>KeepLive · Não somos afiliados ao TikTok</p>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
